{"tid":629787,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"娜姐攞獎死而無憾","createTime":"2018-04-15T04:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T06:09:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6458a90a54ed4c33971268f4d45b65f15bf07728","tid":629787,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:07:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180415/20361756?_ga=2.115993478.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F20361756%3F_ga%3D2.115993478.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=e2PC5uQKZy0AmFTAHjyWphFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=c30e0a63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F20361756%3F_ga%3D2.115993478.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=66a63da0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180415/20361756?_ga=2.115993478.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n娜姐攞獎死而無憾<br />\n<br />\n3.2K<br />\n娛樂名人<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n娜姐坦承想攞影后，更笑言奪獎死而無憾。攝影：仇志德<br />\n<br />\n周秀娜憑《29+1》首度提名影后，她自言接戲之時剛好30歲：「我29+1時正正要拍《29+1》，記得當日收到呢個古仔，我未有感受到女人三十係一個關口，但越投入角色，越發現原來自己都係咁，真人同情節互相影響，我都似戲中嘅林若君。」她表示要多謝導演彭秀慧在緣份到的時候找她演出，年紀太大或太年輕，在閱歷或心境上未必得出如今的效果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180415/large/15ec6p7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180415%2Flarge%2F15ec6p7e.jpg&h=10e45bcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n娜姐演出《29+1》越拍越投入，發現自己似戲中的角色。劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180415/large/15ec6p8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180415%2Flarge%2F15ec6p8e.jpg&h=cf5d941a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n娜姐感謝導演彭秀慧（右），在她踏入30歲時拍《29+1》。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有代表作永遠保存<br />\n<br />\n有提名而緊張是理所當然，娜姐直言：「我𠵱家用感恩心態去睇呢件事，難以想像。今年入行第10年，可以去到金像獎係好有紀念價值，我一定用心參與頒獎禮。冇去諗有冇信心，入圍已經覺得係執到。」<br />\n<br />\n娜姐只看過周迅的入圍片，她說：「冇話睇好邊個，全部好犀利，真係好難揀，個個都有機會。要揀一個一定唔會揀自己，直覺我揀毛姐。當然都想拎『最佳女主角』，攞咗死而無憾，但真心講拍戲唔係為想攞獎，要揀好劇本。我鍾意電影，可以永遠保存落嚟，有一個代表角色，永遠可以睇番。」跟Stephy一樣，娜姐被指擺脫花瓶形象，未來希望有機會演性格分裂的精神病患者。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：陳杰<br />\n髮型：Amber Tse of Queens Private I<br />\n化妝：Circle Cheung of <a href=\"http://ndnco.co\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fndnco.co&d=e2PC5uQKZy0AmFTAHjyWphFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=8b20c034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ndnco.co</a><br />\n服裝提供：Versace<br />\n場地提供：PLAY HKPOP<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n毛舜筠了解對手<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n鄭中基若封帝感謝太太<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n凌文龍佛系爭獎<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n被毛舜筠演技震撼視為勁敵Stephy爭影后：未識得緊張<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晚 2000-2330 第37屆香港電影金像獎頒獎典禮 ViuTV 99台 (4月15日 星期日)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/629720/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/629720/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"557745a8c4f4ef492765259a219b9570d450c39a","tid":629787,"uid":8007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:13:37.000Z","msg":"佢呢套真係做得幾好<br />\n睇之前都唔知佢識做戲 可能咁反差大"},{"pid":"a8082049793ad1c30936438a1f3d6f43d495e8a2","tid":629787,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T06:09:48.000Z","msg":"周秀娜你今次重唔死"}]}